00:01:17.963 --> 00:01:18.529
Probably so.

00:01:18.529 --> 00:01:19.203
I don't know.

00:01:19.203 --> 00:01:21.197
“Here comes Tommy to the mound. Hold on a minute.”

00:01:21.197 --> 00:01:22.213
“That's not Tommy.”

00:01:22.213 --> 00:01:24.939
“That looks a lot like Don Rickles taking the pitcher out.”

00:01:24.939 --> 00:01:27.707
