two bullets in the head Thursday.

00:04:10.921 --> 00:04:13.649
[Laughing]

00:04:13.649 --> 00:04:15.690
We had some good times together, yeah.

00:04:15.690 --> 00:04:17.118
We did. I miss him.

00:04:17.118 --> 00:04:21.569
